Code.Terraform:
```hcl
# Terraform: Set Cognito temporary password expiration to 7 days or less
resource "aws_cognito_user_pool" "<example_resource_name>" {
  name = "<example_resource_name>"

  password_policy {
    temporary_password_validity_days = 7  # Critical: 7 or less to pass the check
  }
}
```
